Our first Parent Univiersity for the year will take place Monday the 13th from 6:00-7:30 at Heritage Middle School. Topics include:

 Anti-Bullying programs and initiatives;
 Social Emotional Curriculum;
 New District-wide assessment STAR;
 2017 PARCC Results;
 Student Online Resources

A light dinner will be provided: Jimmy Johns’ sandwiches, chips, cookies and drink. Raffle prizes will be available.

https://drive.google.com/open?id=1-zLgSB8XuWI_GS0LrBkHnpdcDf2LC6vX

